# Config & Modes
- Live/paper mode is stored in `system.mode` of [config/trading_config.json](mdc:config/trading_config.json). Use `config_manager.get_mode()`/`set_mode()`.
- Do not use `trading.mode`. The engine listens to `system.mode` changes.
- Handy getters: `get_trading_config`, `get_monitoring_config`, `get_risk_management_config`.
- System/trading toggles: `config_manager.enable_system/disable_system`, `enable_trading/disable_trading`.
